snippet.title: REVEREND | FREE RETRO FPS/BOOMER SHOOTER | EARLY ACCESS TRAILER
snippet.description:
PLAY THE GAME FOR FREE: https://twisted-sickle.itch.io/reverend-game
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A project I'm working on mostly for my own amusement, and to develop a few skills.

Follow Twisted Sickle on Itch.io for updates, dev diaries and (of couse) the game itself!

I would love to hear your feedback - please, leave it either down in the comments here, or over on Itch.io!

Music by Frej Wentzell Samuelsson/Boombox Murders
